node.text:
/// @noravexplora & @clubmaiteee catch up about the inspirational women in their lives highlighted through the personal touches to their upcoming signature colorways.

The Gazelle ADV by Nora & Samba ADV by Maité are available March 16th in select skate shops, online at adidas.com/skateboarding and on the adidas CONFIRMED app.
 
#adidasSkateboarding #IWD #InternationalWomensDay 
🎥 @torstenfrank @samuelmcguire

node.text:
No trips. No problem. @LucasPuig spends some quality time at home in Biarritz, France doing what he does best. Catch the PUIG landing in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding September 19th.
•
#adidasSkateboarding #LucasPuig #LaMarqueAux3Bandes 🎥 @torstenfrank

node.text:
TYSHAWN Low /// A nod to his debut signature Pro Model colorway from 2017, the Tyshawn Low arrives in a premium white leather and suede upper accented by the same collegiate green stripes, while maintaining classic skateboarding aesthetics with an added suede toe cap for extended durability. Carrying the same DNA as his debut signature model, an EVA midsole and inner vulc wrap provide continuous support and high-impact absorption. As a step towards the brand’s ongoing journey to End Plastic Waste, the TYSHAWN Low comes with a more sustainable moisture-wicking PU sockliner created from recycled materials that offers extra breathability and anti-microbial properties. Rounding out design details is the updated Tyshawn
Trefoil logo mark emblazoned in gold on a form-fitting memory foam tongue for a custom fit providing ultimate comfort. The all-new TYSHAWN Low is available now in select skate shops and at adidas.com/Tyshawn
•
#adidasSkateboarding #TYSHAWN
